Who We Are

Alpha Zeta is USC's premier co-ed professional business fraternity, dedicated to fostering lifelong brotherhood and preparing members for successful careers. Through our signature AZ Groups program, mentorship network, and social events, we cultivate leaders who excel both professionally and personally.

Where Our Members Work

Our Values

The principles that guide everything we do at Alpha Zeta

Brotherhood

Cultivating lifelong connections and unwavering support among members.

Integrity

Upholding the highest ethical standards in all endeavors.

Excellence

Pursuing continuous growth and professional development.

Unity

Promoting collaboration and a shared sense of purpose.

Service

Dedicating time and resources to positively impact the community.
